To set up the requested infrastructure, we will define a custom VPC with two subnets in different Availability Zones (a requirement for AWS RDS Subnet Groups), a Security Group allowing PostgreSQL traffic, and finally the RDS instance itself with the specified storage and maintenance window configurations.

