The `aws_glacier_vault_lock` resource is used to manage the lock state. By setting `complete_lock = true`, the lock becomes immutable after the 24-hour grace period defined by AWS.

```hcl
# Configure the AWS Provider
terraform {
  required_providers {
    aws = {
      source  = "hashicorp/aws"
      version = "~> 5.0"
