To fulfill your request, I will define a VPC with two public subnets distributed across two different availability zones. I will then configure an Internet Gateway and a Route Table to allow internet access. Finally, I will create a Security Group specifically for MySQL and PostgreSQL traffic, and a Database Subnet Group required for RDS deployments.

```hcl
# Terraform Provider Configuration
terraform {
  required_providers {
    aws = {
      source  = "hashicorp/aws"
